oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Elsie McWilliams recording with discussion by Prynce Wheeler
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A cappella performance by Elsie McWilliams of I'm Sending You 1000 Red Roses Dear, followed by Prynce Wheeler discussing the recording in a message to Jim Evans. Followed by Prynce Wheeler performing Chained To My Memories Of You.
